text: Kazayak-Khusnullino () is a rural locality (a village) in Krasnovoskhodsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 53 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 95 km from Iglino, 10 km from Krasny Voskhod. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Kazayak-Khusnullino
